init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The US was not the only country to be fooled, as many countries around the world were in the same situation.

actions.name: text-delete

actions.text: , had managed to recuperate its losses and had become a world power once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: However, the US did not want to be left behind, and decided to form its own alliance with other countries that were also deceived.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The US alliance, which was later named the Allied Nations, was a powerful force, and quickly became the most powerful alliance in the world.
